<div style="font-size:15px;" class="alert alert-info">
	<strong>제1325회 손이 시려</strong></div>

<table style="font-size:15px;">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td style="padding: 5px; height: 30px; font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: #3f7dba;">A : </span>
Do you possibly have <span style="color: white;border-bottom:1px solid #922B21" >hand</span> <span style="color: white;border-bottom:1px solid #922B21" >warmers</span>?</td>
<td style="color: #848484; font-weight: bold;">혹시 손난로 있나요?</td>
	</tr>
<tr>
<td style="padding: 5px; height: 30px; font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: #3f7dba;">A : </span>
My <span style="color: white;border-bottom:1px solid #922B21" >hands</span> are freezing.</td>
<td style="color: #848484; font-weight: bold;">손이 시려서요.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="padding: 5px; height: 30px; font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: #d16821;">B : </span>
Yes, but you have to be <span style="color: white;border-bottom:1px solid #922B21"  >careful</span>.</td>
<td style="color: #848484; font-weight: bold;">있긴 한데 조심하셔야 해요.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="padding: 5px; height: 30px; font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: #d16821;">B : </span>
You might <span style="color: white;border-bottom:1px solid #922B21" >burn</span> yourself.</td>
<td style="color: #848484; font-weight: bold;">화상을 입으실지도 몰라요.</td>
</tr>

</tbody>
</table>

<p></p>

<div style="font-size:15px;float:left;">

<ul>

<li>possibly = 혹시
    <ul>
	<li style="list-style-type:circle;">Do you possibly know this guy?</li>
    </ul>
</li>
<li><span style="font-weight: bold;">hand warmer</span> : 손난로<br>
= hand (손) + warmer (따뜻하게 만드는 것)</li>

<li><span style="font-weight: bold;">hand</span> : 손
    <ul>
	<li style="list-style-type:circle;">foot : 발 / feet : 발 [복수]</li>
    </ul>
</li>
<li>freeze = 얼다
    <ul>
	<li style="list-style-type:circle;">My feet are freezing.</li>
    </ul>
</li>

<li>have to (동사원형) = (동사원형)해야만 한다
    <ul>
	<li style="list-style-type:circle;">You have to come to work.</li>
	<li style="list-style-type:circle;">We have to walk quietly.</li>
    </ul>
</li>
<li><span style="font-weight: bold;">careful</span> : 조심하는</li>

<li>might (동사원형) = 어쩌면 (동사원형)할지도 모른다
    <ul>
	<li style="list-style-type:circle;">Kenny might be lonely.</li>
    </ul>
</li>
<li><span style="font-weight: bold;">burn</span> : 화상을 입히다, 태우다 [r 발음 주의]
    <ul>
	<li style="list-style-type:circle;">turn / earn / pattern</li>
    </ul>
</li>
<li>burn oneself : 스스로를 화상 입히다 → 화상을 입다
    <ul>
	<li style="list-style-type:circle;">yourself : 네 자신, 네 스스로</li>
    </ul>
</li>


</ul>

</div>
